# =============================================================================
# STAGING NOTES
# =============================================================================
# 1. This staging environment runs on port 3001 (different from development)
# 2. Points to staging backend on port 8001
# 3. Uses test credentials for external services
# 4. Can run in parallel with development environment
# 5. Perfect for testing new features before production
# 6. All analytics are in test mode with enhanced logging